---
description: Documentation layer placement rules
alwaysApply: true
---

Place content by layer:
- manifest/ — business requirements and acceptance criteria
- docs/developer/approach/ — workflow and rationale
- docs/developer/architecture/ — solution-independent strategy
- docs/user/ — complete end-user documentation
- docs/admin/ — operations; link to user docs, do not duplicate

Epics belong in manifest/Deep-Backlog.md, not ROADMAP ## slots.
